
https://www.linode.com/docs/guides/using-ssh-agent/

run below command in your terminal

eval `ssh-agent`

ssh-add ~/.ssh/id_rsa

or

ssh-add ~/.ssh/my_key


After doing above you need not to mention pem key details in Ansible.cfg file



